title: 820-00165 wont run off battery
message:
Arrived with liquid damage but none near u7000 or battery connector.

OSX recognizes and charges battery but wont run off the battery. R7006 is good

PPBUS_G3H on battery alone 3.8V

Changed u7000 and Q7155 no change.

Diode mode on SMBUS_SMC_SDA/SCL lines is good

Using known good battery.

Should SMC be changed next??

title: 820-00165 wont run off battery
message:
I suppose you've meant U7100 all the time.

"PPBUS_G3H on battery alone 3.8V"
Did you try known good battery?
If battery is really charged, there should be higher value?
Does the percentage increases, when charging?

Be sure R6950 is good.
Check if J6950 is not half broken; saw this few times.

title: 820-00165 wont run off battery
message:
yes using known good battery and percentage is 100. 

R6950 is good

J6950 is in perfect shape

title: 820-00165 wont run off battery
message: What is battery voltage at the battery connector (without charger)?
